<h4>Our Mission</h4>
<p>Our goal for this site is to give people with dietary restrictions and food allergies multiple options at restaurants and for recipes. We hope to spread the news of different brands and food chains that offer different options for them as well as showing the different subsitutions they can use when cooking.</p>

