      <img src="images/Gluten-free.jpg" alt>
      <p> Gluten is a name for proteins found in things like wheat and barley.  People who are gluten-free cannot eat anything containing wheat products, or in extreme cases, anything contaminated by wheat. People who are gluten-free tend to avoid bread, pasta, cereals, and baked goods. </p>
